Any place that cracks my lobster claws for me deserves 5 stars and a nice tip!!!   This waiter was great!!!   We started with 2 crab claws that did not provide very much meat. This was okay with us, because when the entrees were served it was clear we did not need an appetizer.   I had lobster stuffed with crab! Yum!! It was cooked perfectly so there was not too much hassle to get the meat out. Then the waiter offered to crack my lobster claws and pulled out this scrumptious piece of meat that was heavenly! Oh my.   My date had surf and turf which is huge. A full prime rib and a full lobster, I think it is meant for 2 people? Delicious none the less.   Everything was great here.

